The class handles the `PlayerItemBreakEvent` event and provides a \\\"preservation\\\" enchantment that prevents the player\\u0027s item from breaking.\\n\\n`Preservation`: A class that implements the \\\"Preservation\\\" enchantment, which prevents the player\\u0027s item from breaking when it would normally break.\\n\\n`onPlayerItemBreak`: A method that is called when a player\\u0027s item breaks, and it checks if the item has the \\\"Preservation\\\" enchantment. information on the player\\u0027s sidebar.\\n\\n`loadOxygenDataFile`: Loads the oxygen data file, creating it if necessary.\\n`saveOxygenData`: Saves the current oxygen levels to the oxygen data oxygen capacity based on their Mining level and Ventilation enchantments.\\n`getOxygenDepletionRate`: Determines the oxygen depletion rate based on the player\\u0027s
